      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>blanched spinach</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>peeled garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to a <strong>food processor </strong>with your <strong>basil</strong>, <strong>ground almonds </strong>and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Add a very generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and blitz until smooth – this is your<strong> almond pesto</strong></p>",
