      "instruction": "<p>Chop (or grate) your <strong>remaining garlic </strong>finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic</strong> with your <strong>tomato paste </strong>in a bowl with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Peel lengths off your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> with a peeler until you end up with a pile of <strong>courgette ribbons</strong>, then<strong> </strong>dice the <strong>remaining inner stem[s]</strong></p><p>Trim the woody ends off your <strong>asparagus</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
