            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top with the <strong>courgette ribbons </strong>and<strong> diced courgette</strong>, then spread over the<strong> almond pesto</strong></p><p>Lay the<strong> asparagus</strong> top to tail over the pesto and season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>then twist the <strong>pastry border</strong> over the edge of the filling (start from one corner and work around in one direction, overlapping the pastry each time)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 25-30 min or until the pastry is golden and cooked through and the edges have puffed up – this is your <strong>asparagus, courgette & almond pesto galette</strong></p>",
