      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>asparagus, courgette & almond pesto galette </strong>in half</p><p>Serve the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>asparagus, courgette & almond pesto galette </strong>with the<strong> lettuce leaves </strong>to the side and top with the<strong> lemon & date vinaigrette</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
